SELECT
  (
    SELECT
      c.Segment
    FROM yearmonth AS ym
    JOIN customers AS c
      ON ym.CustomerID = c.CustomerID
    WHERE
      c.Currency = 'EUR' AND substr(ym.Date, 1, 4) = '2013'
    GROUP BY
      c.Segment
    ORDER BY
      SUM(ym.Consumption) DESC

    JOIN customers AS c
      ON ym.CustomerID = c.CustomerID
    WHERE
      c.Currency = 'EUR' AND substr(ym.Date, 1, 4) = '2012'

      c.Segment
    ORDER BY
      SUM(ym.Consumption)
    LIMIT 1
  ) AS Lowest_Increase_Segment;	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
